p://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1034, \"end\": 1040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\", \"score\": 0.9999954596008441, \"rank\": 4.540385673743991e-06, \"text\": \"Madrid\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fifth-place finish\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 1001}, {\"ngram\": \"the HSBC SVNS Grand Final\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"the weekend\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1055}, {\"ngram\": \"Keenan\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1063}, {\"ngram\": \"the province\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"the Champions Cup\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1182}, {\"ngram\": \"the season\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1196}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These opportunities do not come around too often,\\\" he said after his first Sevens appearance in five years.\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1307, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These opportunities\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1219}, {\"ngram\": \"his first Sevens appearance\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1292}, {\"ngram\": \"five years\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1306}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had to make a tough decision, but hopefully, it's one that I will not regret and I will fully commit now over the next few weeks and see what happens.\\\"\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1463, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tough decision\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1340}, {\"ngram\": \"the next few weeks\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having brushed off questions about returning to Sevensin the aftermath of Antoine Dupont's switch to the code last January, the 27-year-old revealed more details of how the move came about.\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1539, \"end\": 1553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antoine_Dupont\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Antoine Dupont\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antoine_Dupont\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antoine_Dupont\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"Sevensin\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1521}, {\"ngram\": \"the aftermath\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1535}, {\"ngram\": \"the code\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1574}, {\"ngram\": \"more details\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1626}, {\"ngram\": \"the move\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1642}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been a very busy year for me, that's the exciting part,\\\" he said in Madrid, where France won the series.\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1766, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1730, \"end\": 1736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\", \"score\": 0.9999954596008441, \"rank\": 4.540385673743991e-06, \"text\": \"Madrid\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\"}, {\"begin\": 1744, \"end\": 1750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9827444877734809, \"rank\": 0.017558455745309703, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very busy year\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1683}, {\"ngram\": \"the exciting part\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1716}, {\"ngram\": \"the series\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I suppose it was put on the table a while back but it was always going to be a bit of a last-minute decision, \\\"I'd been injured since the Six Nations and that threw a bit of a spanner in the works.\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1967, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1802}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 1851}, {\"ngram\": \"a last-minute decision\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"the Six Nations\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1918}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1939}, {\"ngram\": \"a spanner\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1952}, {\"ngram\": \"the works\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 1965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Prior to that, I was trying to just focus on Leinster and the Champions Cup because that's where my career is and where I had to fully focus and commit 100%.\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2015, \"end\": 2023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leinster_Rugby\", \"score\": 0.999999999984766, \"rank\": 1.307888467003936e-11, \"text\": \"Leinster\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leinster_Rugby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leinster_Rugby\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Champions Cup\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2045}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2076}, {\"ngram\": \"100%\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2126}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The opportunity came about pretty late on and because the lads were doing so well this year, I had a few chats with a few coaches, a few of the actual playing squad and everybody seemed keen to get me on board.\\\"\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2341, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The opportunity\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2145}, {\"ngram\": \"the lads\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2192}, {\"ngram\": \"a few chats\", \"from\": 2229, \"to\": 2240}, {\"ngram\": \"a few coaches\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2259}, {\"ngram\": \"the actual playing squad\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2294}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2308}, {\"ngram\": \"board\", \"from\"